<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>UX-Men</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="../../images/favicon.ico" type="image/png"></head>
<body>

<%- include('../../shared/components/header/header') %>


<div class="block poster">
    <div class="block__wrapper poster__wrapper">
        <h1 class="poster__movie-title movie-title movie-title--clipped">UX-Men</h1>
        <button class="button poster__button">Read the Story</button>
    </div>
</div>


<section class="story">

    <div class="begin-story">

        <div class="begin-story__container">

            <img src="../../images/landing/icon-heart.svg" alt="" class="begin-story__icon-love">

            <div class="begin-story__description">
                <p class="begin-story__description-paragraph">For many years people and programmers had lived in
                    harmony.
                    Without wars
                    and code reviews.</p>
                <p class="begin-story__description-paragraph">But once...</p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>


    <div class="no-likes">

        <div class="block__wrapper no-likes__container">

            <p class="no-likes__description"> ...something horrible did happen – likes from all social media had
                suddenly started to disappear. And there was no possibility to like you friends’ pictures and no
                possibility
                to see who appreciated your posts. There was none. The panic broke out. The world was standing on
                the
                verge
                of a total collapse. And this is how our story begins.</p>


            <div class="no-likes__img-wrapper">
                <img src="../../images/landing/nobodylikesyou.png" alt="" class="no-likes__img">

                <div class="no-likes__left-tear no-likes__left-tear1"></div>
                <div class="no-likes__left-tear no-likes__left-tear2"></div>
                <div class="no-likes__left-tear no-likes__left-tear3"></div>
                <div class="no-likes__left-tear no-likes__left-tear4"></div>
                <div class="no-likes__left-tear no-likes__left-tear5"></div>

                <div class="no-likes__right-tear no-likes__right-tear1"></div>
                <div class="no-likes__right-tear no-likes__right-tear2"></div>
                <div class="no-likes__right-tear no-likes__right-tear3"></div>
                <div class="no-likes__right-tear no-likes__right-tear4"></div>
                <div class="no-likes__right-tear no-likes__right-tear5"></div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story__button-wrapper">
        <button class="button story__button">Continue reading</button>
    </div>

</section>



<section class="block team">
    <div class="block__wrapper team__container">
        <div class="team__text-container">
            <div class="team__story-text team__story-text--text1 story-text">
                The governments around the globe gathered behind closed doors to find a solution. There was no time
                for second thoughts.
            </div>
            <div class="team__story-text team__story-text--text2 story-text">
                It was instantly decided to create a <span class="team__story-text--decorate">Fast React Team</span> of the most powerful
                <span class="team__story-text--decorate">UX-Men</span> on Earth for this mission.
            </div>
            <div class="team__story-text team__story-text--text3 story-text">
                To stop Bugman and ruin his plans UX-Men have to fight all bugs and go to the most <span class="team__story-text--decorate">dangerous</span> and
                <span class="team__story-text--decorate">unexplainable place</span>  of the Internet – to <span class="team__story-text--decorate">Odnoklassniki</span>, to find an intact piece of code and heal all
                other social media with it.
            </div>
            <div class="team__story-text team__story-text--text4 story-text">
                But who are they, our heroes?
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team__button-container">
            <button class="button team__button team__button--clicked">Meet The Team</button>
            <button class="button team__button">Continue reading</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="deadline">
    <div class="block__wrapper deadline__container">
        <div class="deadline__title"></div>
        <ul class="timer">
            <li class="timer__item"><span id="days" class="timer__date"></span>days</li>
            <li class="timer__item"><span id="hours" class="timer__date"></span>Hours</li>
            <li class="timer__item"><span id="minutes" class="timer__date"></span>Minutes</li>
            <li class="timer__item"><span id="seconds" class="timer__date"></span>Seconds</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="deadline__button-container">
            <button class="button deadline__button">You cannot stay aside!</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>